{
  "video_id": "dKq34EVggjI",
  "title": "Bridges should be beautiful | Ian Firth",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13440.0,
      "end_time": 16400.0,
      "text": "The world needs bridges."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17920.0,
      "end_time": 21400.0,
      "text": "Have you ever thought about what it would be like not to have any?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21880.0,
      "end_time": 25160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s hard to imagine a civilization without bridges"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25400.0,
      "end_time": 26416.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;re so essential"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26440.0,
      "end_time": 29176.0,
      "text": "for growth and development of human society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29200.0,
      "end_time": 33120.0,
      "text": "but they&#39;re not just about a safe way across a river or an obstacle."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 35720.0,
      "end_time": 38976.0,
      "text": "They shout about connectivity --"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39000.0,
      "end_time": 40200.0,
      "text": "community."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40960.0,
      "end_time": 42856.0,
      "text": "They reveal something about creativity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42880.0,
      "end_time": 44950.0,
      "text": "our ingenuity --"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44119.0,
      "end_time": 46440.0,
      "text": "they even hint at our identity."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 49240.0,
      "end_time": 51496.0,
      "text": "And when bridges fail,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 51520.0,
      "end_time": 53416.0,
      "text": "or are destroyed in conflict,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 53440.0,
      "end_time": 55216.0,
      "text": "communities struggle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 55240.0,
      "end_time": 57240.0,
      "text": "development stagnates, people suffer."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59280.0,
      "end_time": 61960.0,
      "text": "Even today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61120.0,
      "end_time": 65150.0,
      "text": "there are over one billion people living in poor, rural communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65400.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66256.0,
      "text": "around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66280.0,
      "end_time": 68216.0,
      "text": "that do not have safe, year-round access"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68240.0,
      "end_time": 70696.0,
      "text": "to the things that you and I take for granted:"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70720.0,
      "end_time": 73280.0,
      "text": "education, medical care, access to markets ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74960.0,
      "end_time": 78136.0,
      "text": "which is why wonderful organizations like Bridges to Prosperity"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 78160.0,
      "end_time": 81216.0,
      "text": "build bridges in this kind of place -- this is in Rwanda."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81240.0,
      "end_time": 83616.0,
      "text": "And they make such a difference,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 83640.0,
      "end_time": 86776.0,
      "text": "not only to those lives immediately around the bridge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86800.0,
      "end_time": 88765.0,
      "text": "but the impact of these bridges is huge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 88790.0,
      "end_time": 91256.0,
      "text": "and it spreads over the whole community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 91280.0,
      "end_time": 92520.0,
      "text": "far, far away."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 94400.0,
      "end_time": 97216.0,
      "text": "Of course bridges have been around for an awfully long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 97240.0,
      "end_time": 101175.0,
      "text": "The oldest ones are stone because it&#39;s a very durable material."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 101200.0,
      "end_time": 102456.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know about you --"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 102480.0,
      "end_time": 104696.0,
      "text": "I love to look at the development of technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 104720.0,
      "end_time": 107560.0,
      "text": "to learn about what people did with the materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 107800.0,
      "end_time": 109360.0,
      "text": "and tools available to them at the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 110200.0,
      "end_time": 113160.0,
      "text": "So the Pont Du Gard in the center is a wonderful example --"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 113400.0,
      "end_time": 115376.0,
      "text": "Roman aqueduct in the South of France --"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 115400.0,
      "end_time": 118976.0,
      "text": "fantastic piece of technology built using massive stones put together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 119000.0,
      "end_time": 121376.0,
      "text": "dry -- there&#39;s no mortar in those joints."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 121400.0,
      "end_time": 123336.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re just dry stone joints --"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 123360.0,
      "end_time": 124576.0,
      "text": "fantastic"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 124600.0,
      "end_time": 126160.0,
      "text": "and almost as good as new today."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 128360.00000000001,
      "end_time": 129976.00000000001,
      "text": "Or sometimes up in the mountains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 130000.0,
      "end_time": 132856.0,
      "text": "people would build these suspension bridges,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 132880.0,
      "end_time": 134656.0,
      "text": "often across some dizzy canyon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 134680.0,
      "end_time": 135896.0,
      "text": "using a vine."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 135920.0,
      "end_time": 137456.0,
      "text": "In this case, this is in Peru."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 137480.0,
      "end_time": 139816.0,
      "text": "This is using grass which grows locally"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 139840.0,
      "end_time": 142560.0,
      "text": "and is woven into ropes to build these bridges."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 142800.0,
      "end_time": 145240.0,
      "text": "And do you know they rebuild this every year?"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 146160.0,
      "end_time": 148600.0,
      "text": "Because of course grass is not a durable material."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 149600.0,
      "end_time": 151720.0,
      "text": "So this bridge is unchanged since Inca times."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 154720.0,
      "end_time": 157240.0,
      "text": "And bridges can be symbols of their location."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 158400.0,
      "end_time": 160856.0,
      "text": "Of course, Golden Gate and Sydney are well familiar."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 160880.0,
      "end_time": 164416.0,
      "text": "In Mostar the bridge was synonymous with the name of the place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 164440.0,
      "end_time": 167936.0,
      "text": "and to such an extent that in the war in 1993"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 167960.0,
      "end_time": 169416.0,
      "text": "when the bridge was destroyed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 169440.0,
      "end_time": 172760.0,
      "text": "the town all but lost its identity until the bridge was reconstructed."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 174000.0,
      "end_time": 177576.0,
      "text": "And bridges are enormous features in our landscape --"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 177600.0,
      "end_time": 179976.0,
      "text": "not just enormous, sometimes there&#39;s small ones --"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 180000.0,
      "end_time": 182696.0,
      "text": "and they are really significant features,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 182720.0,
      "end_time": 186600.0,
      "text": "and I believe we have a duty to make our bridges beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 188320.0,
      "end_time": 189656.0,
      "text": "Thankfully, many people do."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 189680.0,
      "end_time": 193576.0,
      "text": "Think of the stunning Millau Viaduct in the South of France."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 193600.0,
      "end_time": 197136.0,
      "text": "French engineer Michel Virlogeux and British architect Lord Foster"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 197160.0,
      "end_time": 199216.0,
      "text": "collaborated together to produce something"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 199240.0,
      "end_time": 202936.0,
      "text": "which is a really spectacular synergy of architecture and engineering."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 202960.0,
      "end_time": 207456.0,
      "text": "Or Robert Maillart&#39;s Salginatobel Bridge in the mountains in Switzerland --"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 207480.0,
      "end_time": 208760.0,
      "text": "absolutely sublime."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 209880.0,
      "end_time": 211960.0,
      "text": "Or more recently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 211120.0,
      "end_time": 214176.0,
      "text": "Laurent Ney&#39;s beautiful and rather delicate bridge"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 214200.0,
      "end_time": 216400.0,
      "text": "for Tintagel Castle in the UK."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 217520.0,
      "end_time": 219736.0,
      "text": "These are spectacular and beautiful designs"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 219760.0,
      "end_time": 221320.0,
      "text": "and we need to see more of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 223400.0,
      "end_time": 226840.0,
      "text": "Bridges can be considered in three convenient categories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 228800.0,
      "end_time": 231296.0,
      "text": "depending on the nature of the structural system"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 231320.0,
      "end_time": 234215.0,
      "text": "that they adopt as their principal support."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 234240.0,
      "end_time": 237376.0,
      "text": "So, bending, of course, is the way a beam will behave --"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 237400.0,
      "end_time": 239120.0,
      "text": "so, beams and bending."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 239880.0,
      "end_time": 244000.0,
      "text": "Or compression is the principal way of operating for an arch."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 244720.0,
      "end_time": 247376.0,
      "text": "Or for the really long spans you need to go lightweight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 247400.0,
      "end_time": 248736.0,
      "text": "as we&#39;ll see in a minute,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 248760.0,
      "end_time": 251416.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;ll use tension, cables --"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 251440.0,
      "end_time": 252896.0,
      "text": "suspension bridges."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 252920.0,
      "end_time": 255200.0,
      "text": "And the opportunity for variety is enormous."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 256399.0,
      "end_time": 259616.0,
      "text": "Engineers have a fantastic scope for innovation and ingenuity"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 259640.0,
      "end_time": 262200.0,
      "text": "and developing different forms around these types."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 265520.0,
      "end_time": 269216.0,
      "text": "But technological change happens relatively slowly in my world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 269240.0,
      "end_time": 270456.0,
      "text": "believe it or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 270480.0,
      "end_time": 275160.0,
      "text": "compared to the changes that happen in mobile phone technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 275400.0,
      "end_time": 277376.0,
      "text": "and computers and digital technologies and so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 277400.0,
      "end_time": 279655.0,
      "text": "In our world of construction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 279680.0,
      "end_time": 282240.0,
      "text": "the changes seem positively glacial."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 284400.0,
      "end_time": 286600.0,
      "text": "And the reason for this can be summarized in one word:"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 288400.0,
      "end_time": 289240.0,
      "text": "risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 290680.0,
      "end_time": 292696.0,
      "text": "Structural engineers like me manage risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 292720.0,
      "end_time": 294696.0,
      "text": "We are responsible for structural safety."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 294720.0,
      "end_time": 295936.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what we do."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 295960.0,
      "end_time": 297816.0,
      "text": "And when we design bridges like these,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 297840.0,
      "end_time": 302736.0,
      "text": "I have to balance the probability that loads will be excessive on one side"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 302760.0,
      "end_time": 305896.0,
      "text": "or the strength will be too low on the other side."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 305920.0,
      "end_time": 309696.0,
      "text": "Both of which, incidentally, are full of uncertainty usually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 309710.0,
      "end_time": 311465.0,
      "text": "and so it&#39;s a probabilistic problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 311490.0,
      "end_time": 312696.0,
      "text": "and we have to make sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 312720.0,
      "end_time": 316560.0,
      "text": "that there&#39;s an adequate margin for safety between the two, of course."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 316800.0,
      "end_time": 318135.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no such thing, I have to tell you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 318160.0,
      "end_time": 319416.0,
      "text": "as absolute safety."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 319440.0,
      "end_time": 321816.0,
      "text": "Contrary to popular belief,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 321840.0,
      "end_time": 323359.0,
      "text": "zero risk doesn&#39;t exist."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 325720.0,
      "end_time": 328776.0,
      "text": "Engineers have to do their calculations and get their sums right"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 328800.0,
      "end_time": 330856.0,
      "text": "to make sure that those margins are there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 330880.0,
      "end_time": 332536.0,
      "text": "and society expects them to do so,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 332560.0,
      "end_time": 335800.0,
      "text": "which is why it&#39;s all the more alarming when things like this happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 339800.0,
      "end_time": 342816.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not going to go into the reasons for these tragedies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 342840.0,
      "end_time": 345176.0,
      "text": "but they are part of the reason"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 345200.0,
      "end_time": 347575.0,
      "text": "why technological change happens quite slowly."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 347600.0,
      "end_time": 348960.0,
      "text": "Nobody wants this to happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 350280.0,
      "end_time": 353239.0,
      "text": "Clients don&#39;t want this to happen on their projects, obviously."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 354120.0,
      "end_time": 356960.0,
      "text": "And yet of course they want innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 356120.0,
      "end_time": 358560.0,
      "text": "Innovation is vital."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 358800.0,
      "end_time": 361560.0,
      "text": "As an engineer, it&#39;s part of my DNA."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 361800.0,
      "end_time": 362895.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s in my blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 362920.0,
      "end_time": 366656.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t be a very good engineer if I wasn&#39;t wanting to innovate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 366680.0,
      "end_time": 369616.0,
      "text": "but we have to do so from a position of knowledge and strength"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 369640.0,
      "end_time": 370880.0,
      "text": "and understanding."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 372800.0,
      "end_time": 373936.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s no good taking a leap in the dark,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 373960.0,
      "end_time": 377416.0,
      "text": "and civilization has learned from mistakes since the beginning of time --"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 377440.0,
      "end_time": 378880.0,
      "text": "no one more so than engineers."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 382400.0,
      "end_time": 384176.0,
      "text": "Some of you may have seen this film before --"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 384200.0,
      "end_time": 386776.0,
      "text": "this is the very famous Tacoma Narrows Bridge collapse"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 386800.0,
      "end_time": 388720.0,
      "text": "in Tacoma, Washington state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 390200.0,
      "end_time": 391400.0,
      "text": "1940."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 392200.0,
      "end_time": 394336.0,
      "text": "The bridge became known as \"Galloping Gertie\""
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 394360.0,
      "end_time": 395616.0,
      "text": "because she -- she?"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 395640.0,
      "end_time": 397416.0,
      "text": "Is a bridge female? I don&#39;t know."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 397440.0,
      "end_time": 400736.0,
      "text": "She was wobbling like this for quite a long time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 400760.0,
      "end_time": 402719.0,
      "text": "and notice this twisting motion."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 403800.0,
      "end_time": 405376.0,
      "text": "The bridge was far too flexible."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 405400.0,
      "end_time": 407655.0,
      "text": "It was designed by a chap called Leon Moisseiff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 407680.0,
      "end_time": 409616.0,
      "text": "no stranger to suspension bridge design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 409640.0,
      "end_time": 412776.0,
      "text": "but in this case he pushed the limits just that little bit too far"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 412800.0,
      "end_time": 414400.0,
      "text": "and paid the price."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 414520.0,
      "end_time": 416895.0,
      "text": "Thankfully, nobody was killed."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 416920.0,
      "end_time": 420736.0,
      "text": "But this bridge collapse stopped suspension bridge development"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 420760.0,
      "end_time": 421960.0,
      "text": "dead in its tracks."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 422680.0,
      "end_time": 426256.0,
      "text": "For 10 years nobody thought about doing another suspension bridge."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 426280.0,
      "end_time": 427535.0,
      "text": "There were none."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 427560.0,
      "end_time": 429416.0,
      "text": "And when they did emerge in the 1950s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 429440.0,
      "end_time": 431393.0,
      "text": "they were an understandable overreaction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 431417.0,
      "end_time": 434736.0,
      "text": "this sort of oversafe response to what had happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 435880.0,
      "end_time": 438280.0,
      "text": "But when it did occur in the mid-60s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 439320.0,
      "end_time": 440936.0,
      "text": "there was indeed a step change --"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 440960.0,
      "end_time": 443816.0,
      "text": "an innovation, a technological step change."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 443840.0,
      "end_time": 445560.0,
      "text": "This is the Severn Bridge in the UK."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 446200.0,
      "end_time": 449616.0,
      "text": "Notice the aerodynamically streamlined cross section"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 449640.0,
      "end_time": 450856.0,
      "text": "in the center there."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 450880.0,
      "end_time": 453616.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also a box which makes it very torsionally stiff --"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 453640.0,
      "end_time": 457496.0,
      "text": "that twisting motion which we saw at Tacoma would not happen here."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 457520.0,
      "end_time": 459135.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s also really lightweight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 459160.0,
      "end_time": 460576.0,
      "text": "and as we&#39;ll see in a moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 460600.0,
      "end_time": 463416.0,
      "text": "lightweight is really important for long spans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 463440.0,
      "end_time": 467160.0,
      "text": "and everybody seems to want us to build longer spans."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 467400.0,
      "end_time": 468896.0,
      "text": "The longest at the moment is in Japan."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 468920.0,
      "end_time": 472816.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just under 2,000 meters -- one span."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 472840.0,
      "end_time": 474950.0,
      "text": "Just under two kilometers."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 474120.0,
      "end_time": 475456.0,
      "text": "The Akashi Kaikyō Bridge."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 475480.0,
      "end_time": 478446.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re currently working on one in Turkey which is a bit longer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 478460.0,
      "end_time": 480656.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;ve designed the Messina Bridge in Italy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 480680.0,
      "end_time": 483656.0,
      "text": "which is just waiting to get started with construction one day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 483680.0,
      "end_time": 484896.0,
      "text": "who knows when."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 484920.0,
      "end_time": 486960.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 486120.0,
      "end_time": 488776.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to come back to Messina in a moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 488800.0,
      "end_time": 493896.0,
      "text": "But the other kind of long-span bridge which uses that tension principle"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 493920.0,
      "end_time": 495256.0,
      "text": "is the cable-stayed bridge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 495280.0,
      "end_time": 496856.0,
      "text": "and we see a lot of these."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 496880.0,
      "end_time": 500536.0,
      "text": "In fact, in China they&#39;re building a whole load of these right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 500560.0,
      "end_time": 504456.0,
      "text": "The longest of these is the Russky Bridge in Vladivostok, Russia --"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 504480.0,
      "end_time": 506256.0,
      "text": "just over 1,100 meters."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 506280.0,
      "end_time": 509775.0,
      "text": "But let me take you back to this question about long-span and lightweight."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 509800.0,
      "end_time": 511856.0,
      "text": "This is using Messina Bridge as an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 511880.0,
      "end_time": 516336.0,
      "text": "The pie chart in the center represents the capacity of the main cables --"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 516360.0,
      "end_time": 518150.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s what holds the bridge up --"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 518390.0,
      "end_time": 519599.0,
      "text": "the capacity of the main cables."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 520400.0,
      "end_time": 523295.0,
      "text": "And notice that 78 percent of that capacity"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 523320.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525960.0,
      "text": "is used up just holding the bridge up."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 527880.0,
      "end_time": 529895.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s only 22 percent of its capacity --"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 529919.0,
      "end_time": 531336.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s less than a quarter --"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 531360.0,
      "end_time": 532616.0,
      "text": "available for the payload,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 532640.0,
      "end_time": 534816.0,
      "text": "the stuff that the bridge is there to support:"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 534840.0,
      "end_time": 536560.0,
      "text": "the railway, the road and so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 538200.0,
      "end_time": 539456.0,
      "text": "And in fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 539480.0,
      "end_time": 542960.0,
      "text": "over 50 percent of that payload --"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 542120.0,
      "end_time": 543536.0,
      "text": "of that dead load --"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 543560.0,
      "end_time": 544935.0,
      "text": "is the cable on its own."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 544960.0,
      "end_time": 546976.0,
      "text": "Just the cable without any bridge deck."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 547000.0,
      "end_time": 549536.0,
      "text": "If we could make that cable lighter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 549560.0,
      "end_time": 551550.0,
      "text": "we could span longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 551800.0,
      "end_time": 554536.0,
      "text": "Right now if we use the high-strength steel wire available to us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 554560.0,
      "end_time": 558160.0,
      "text": "we can span, practically speaking, around about five or six kilometers"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 558400.0,
      "end_time": 559280.0,
      "text": "if we really push it."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 560480.0,
      "end_time": 563536.0,
      "text": "But if we could use carbon fiber in those cables,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 563560.0,
      "end_time": 565439.0,
      "text": "we could go more than 10 kilometers."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 566560.0,
      "end_time": 567800.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s pretty spectacular."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 570200.0,
      "end_time": 574896.0,
      "text": "But of course superspans is not necessarily the way to go everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 574920.0,
      "end_time": 576136.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re very expensive"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 576160.0,
      "end_time": 579303.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;ve got all sorts of other challenges associated with them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 579327.0,
      "end_time": 580776.0,
      "text": "and we tend to build multispan"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 580800.0,
      "end_time": 583280.0,
      "text": "when we&#39;re crossing a wide estuary or a sea crossing."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 584800.0,
      "end_time": 587496.0,
      "text": "But of course if that sea crossing were somewhere like Gibraltar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 587520.0,
      "end_time": 589976.0,
      "text": "or in this case, the Red Sea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 590000.0,
      "end_time": 594456.0,
      "text": "we would indeed be building multiple superlong spans"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 594480.0,
      "end_time": 597376.0,
      "text": "and that would be something spectacular, wouldn&#39;t it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 597400.0,
      "end_time": 600456.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t think I&#39;m going to see that one finished in my lifetime,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 600480.0,
      "end_time": 603520.0,
      "text": "but it will certainly be worth waiting for for some of you guys."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 604800.0,
      "end_time": 608295.0,
      "text": "Well, I want to tell you about something which I think is really exciting."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 608320.0,
      "end_time": 612816.0,
      "text": "This is a multispan suspension bridge across very deep water in Norway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 612840.0,
      "end_time": 614760.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re working on this at the moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 615400.0,
      "end_time": 619216.0,
      "text": "The deep water means that foundations are prohibitively expensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 619240.0,
      "end_time": 621480.0,
      "text": "So this bridge floats."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 623240.0,
      "end_time": 625496.0,
      "text": "This is a floating, multispan suspension bridge."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 625520.0,
      "end_time": 628199.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve had floating bridges before, but nothing like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 629400.0,
      "end_time": 630616.0,
      "text": "It stands on floating pontoons"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 630640.0,
      "end_time": 632976.0,
      "text": "which are tethered to the seabed and held down --"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 633000.0,
      "end_time": 636960.0,
      "text": "so, pulled down against those buoyancy forces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 636120.0,
      "end_time": 637696.0,
      "text": "and in order to make it stable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 637720.0,
      "end_time": 640416.0,
      "text": "the tops of the towers have to be tied together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 640440.0,
      "end_time": 643216.0,
      "text": "otherwise the whole thing would just wobble around"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 643240.0,
      "end_time": 644936.0,
      "text": "and nobody will want to go on that."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 644960.0,
      "end_time": 646576.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m really excited about this"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 646600.0,
      "end_time": 649176.0,
      "text": "because if you think about the places around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 649200.0,
      "end_time": 650456.0,
      "text": "where the water is so deep"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 650480.0,
      "end_time": 653736.0,
      "text": "that nobody has given a second thought to the possibility of a bridge"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 653760.0,
      "end_time": 655560.0,
      "text": "or any kind of crossing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 655800.0,
      "end_time": 656920.0,
      "text": "this now opens up that possibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 658600.0,
      "end_time": 661640.0,
      "text": "So this one&#39;s being done by the Norwegian Roads Administration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 662600.0,
      "end_time": 664560.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;m really excited to know"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 664800.0,
      "end_time": 666576.0,
      "text": "where else will this technology enable development --"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 666600.0,
      "end_time": 668616.0,
      "text": "that growing together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 668640.0,
      "end_time": 669960.0,
      "text": "that building of community."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 673720.0,
      "end_time": 674960.0,
      "text": "Now, what about concrete?"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 676160.0,
      "end_time": 678480.0,
      "text": "Concrete gets a pretty bad name sometimes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 680800.0,
      "end_time": 683696.0,
      "text": "but in the hands of people like Rudy Ricciotti here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 683720.0,
      "end_time": 685120.0,
      "text": "look what you can do with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 686400.0,
      "end_time": 689856.0,
      "text": "This is what we call ultra-high performance fiber-reinforced concrete."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 689880.0,
      "end_time": 691120.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a bit of a mouthful."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 691680.0,
      "end_time": 693575.0,
      "text": "Us engineers love those kinds of words."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 693600.0,
      "end_time": 695856.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 695880.0,
      "end_time": 697256.0,
      "text": "But what you do with this --"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 697280.0,
      "end_time": 699736.0,
      "text": "this is really superstrong, and it&#39;s really durable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 699750.0,
      "end_time": 702110.0,
      "text": "and you can get this fantastic sculptural quality."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 703200.0,
      "end_time": 704880.0,
      "text": "Who said concrete bridges are dull?"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 707680.0,
      "end_time": 710815.0,
      "text": "We could talk about all sorts of other new technologies and things"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 710840.0,
      "end_time": 712560.0,
      "text": "which are going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 712800.0,
      "end_time": 714296.0,
      "text": "robots and 3-D printing and AI and all of that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 714320.0,
      "end_time": 717654.0,
      "text": "but I want to take you back to something which I alluded to earlier on."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 719518.0,
      "end_time": 721376.0,
      "text": "Our bridges need to be functional, yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 721400.0,
      "end_time": 723960.0,
      "text": "They need to be safe -- absolutely."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 723120.0,
      "end_time": 725400.0,
      "text": "They need to be serviceable and durable."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 725880.0,
      "end_time": 728296.0,
      "text": "But I passionately believe they need to be elegant;"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 728320.0,
      "end_time": 729559.0,
      "text": "they need to be beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 732360.0,
      "end_time": 734320.0,
      "text": "Our bridges are designed for a long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 735280.0,
      "end_time": 737960.0,
      "text": "We tend to design for 100 years plus."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 737120.0,
      "end_time": 739520.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re going to be there for an awfully long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 740480.0,
      "end_time": 742736.0,
      "text": "Nobody is going to remember the cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 742760.0,
      "end_time": 745240.0,
      "text": "Nobody will remember whether it overran a few months."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 746240.0,
      "end_time": 748800.0,
      "text": "But if it&#39;s ugly or just dull,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 749400.0,
      "end_time": 751136.0,
      "text": "it will always be ugly or dull."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 751160.0,
      "end_time": 752959.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 754400.0,
      "end_time": 755280.0,
      "text": "Bridges --"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 756320.0,
      "end_time": 758536.0,
      "text": "beauty enriches life."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 758560.0,
      "end_time": 759760.0,
      "text": "Doesn&#39;t it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 760640.0,
      "end_time": 762376.0,
      "text": "It enhances our well-being."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 762400.0,
      "end_time": 764760.0,
      "text": "Ugliness and mediocrity does exactly the opposite."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 765640.0,
      "end_time": 769656.0,
      "text": "And if we go on building mediocre, ugly environments --"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 769680.0,
      "end_time": 772400.0,
      "text": "and I believe we&#39;re becoming numb to that stuff --"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 773880.0,
      "end_time": 775136.0,
      "text": "if we go on doing that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 775160.0,
      "end_time": 778415.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s something like a large-scale vandalism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 778440.0,
      "end_time": 780400.0,
      "text": "which is completely unacceptable."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 781440.0,
      "end_time": 786376.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 786400.0,
      "end_time": 788336.0,
      "text": "This is a bridge in Lyon in France,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 788360.0,
      "end_time": 791536.0,
      "text": "which was procured through a design competition."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 791560.0,
      "end_time": 795415.0,
      "text": "And I think we need to start talking to those people who procure our bridges"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 795440.0,
      "end_time": 796696.0,
      "text": "and our structures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 796720.0,
      "end_time": 799576.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s the procurement which is often the key."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 799600.0,
      "end_time": 801936.0,
      "text": "Design competitions is one way to get good design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 801960.0,
      "end_time": 803226.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s not the only one."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 803240.0,
      "end_time": 805296.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s an awful lot of procurement going on"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 805320.0,
      "end_time": 807680.0,
      "text": "that is absolutely prejudiced against good design."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 809280.0,
      "end_time": 812640.0,
      "text": "So yes, technology happens a bit slowly sometimes in my world."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 814480.0,
      "end_time": 816920.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m really excited about what we can do with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 818160.0,
      "end_time": 820216.0,
      "text": "Whether it&#39;s saving lives in rural Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 820240.0,
      "end_time": 822696.0,
      "text": "or stretching the boundaries of long-span technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 822720.0,
      "end_time": 825000.0,
      "text": "or just crossing the road next-door,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 827400.0,
      "end_time": 830815.0,
      "text": "I hope we continue to build elegant and beautiful stuff"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 830840.0,
      "end_time": 833800.0,
      "text": "that save lives and build communities."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 835800.0,
      "end_time": 836296.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 836320.0,
      "end_time": 840000.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}